## üé® Paleta de Cores Sugeridas

### Certificados Acad√™micos
- **Azul/√çndigo**: `from-blue-50 to-indigo-50` / `from-blue-600 to-indigo-700`
- **Roxo/Rosa**: `from-purple-50 to-pink-50` / `from-purple-600 to-pink-700`
- **Verde/Teal**: `from-green-50 to-teal-50` / `from-green-600 to-teal-600`
- **Laranja/Vermelho**: `from-orange-50 to-red-50` / `from-orange-600 to-red-600`

### Certificados Complementares
Mesmas cores, mas prefira usar `bg-white dark:bg-slate-800` para fundo branco

